你射架飛機落黎你陪唔陪得起"},{"pid":"dc0f158086d418f5e67fedc0639116c7db82bb77","tid":232751,"uid":80792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T06:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>控唔穩，動作唔熟，點快?</blockquote><br />\n唔淨止控波穩唔穩 <br />\n係做任何動作既速度都唔夠快<br />\n<br />\n係咪真係因為肌肉力量唔夠?<br />\n但有時見D細路動作都可以好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細路都可以有力"},{"pid":"521f75726610c9481d866f5a190fdf31be8a3993","tid":232751,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T06:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩手指陀羅</blockquote><br />\n試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家踢到成個學"},{"pid":"8491d5a244c429c54d0f5591dc1d4f7f2e54bf1d","tid":232751,"uid":62017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T06:45:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>控唔穩，動作唔熟，點快?</blockquote><br />\n唔淨止控波穩唔穩 <br />\n係做任何動作既速度都唔夠快<br />\n<br />\n係咪真係因為肌肉力量唔夠?<br />\n但有時見D細路動作都可以好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細路都可以有力</blockquote><br />\n我只係覺得動作速度同肌肉力量關係唔大<br />\n好多人射波好大力 <br />\n但動作一樣好生硬 好慢"},{"pid":"74b8f3b63a0231301418cefe94d718ce8b8cf3b9","tid":232751,"uid":62017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T06:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>傳 ： 接波前已經要知隊友響邊<br />\n控 ： 練地波就對住牆傳波接波  控高波就要同人練</blockquote><br />\n高波你掉個波上天練痴波咪得</blockquote><br />\n咁樣練係練唔到個波迎面黎個時你點控</blockquote><br />\n如果一人齊練 可以斬波比你控就最好<br />\n但係問題搵唔到人 <br />\n自己一個真係唔知點練"},{"pid":"aa4d2dccb8fadbbd772e30789dd162104b4c3ec9","tid":232751,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:00:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>玩手指陀羅</blockquote><br />\n試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家踢到成個禾確特咁快</blockquote